<title type="html"><![CDATA[01/26(Thu) 'Permacrisis' is Collins dictionary's word of 2022/ Lunar new year holiday  (Host: zoe)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=692&amp;p=720#p720"><![CDATA[
01/26(Thu) 'Permacrisis' is Collins dictionary's word of 2022/ lunar new year holiday  (Host: zoe)<br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:10 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40 pm Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />--------------------------------------------<br /><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Session 1</span><br />'Permacrisis' Is Collins Dictionary's Word of 2022<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-63458467">https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-63458467</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1.Do you agree with the Collins Dictionary choosing “The word ‘permacrisis’ to describe 2022?<br />2.Do you think the world is going to get better soon? Please discuss.<br />3.Which of the words on Collins' list for 2022 did you find interesting?<br />4.What would you say was the most significant event that occurred in 2022?<br />5.Are there any words or phrases in Taiwan that have recently become more commonly used?<br /><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Session 2</span><br />Feel free to talk about &quot; How did you celebrate Lunar New Year&quot; ?    (There is no  article provided)<br /><br />Questions:<br />1.How did you celebrate your Lunar new year‘s eve? <br />2.which of the traditional new year customs do you miss most?<br />3.What is your family’s  traditional new year dinner meal?<br />4.Do you know any special traditions to celebrate new year in other countries?<br />5.     What is your 2023 New Year’s resolution(s)?<br /><br /><br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放的心與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=55735">zoe</a> — Fri Jan 20, 2023 11:19 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
